# Suka Smart Assistant — Cleaning System Scratch Plan
# Style: BLUF + actionable checklists + event hooks

0) BLUF
- Build an intuitive Cleaning flow with:
  • Zone-based + Batch cleaning sessions (room-by-room or “power hour”).
  • Smart chore lists with step-by-step instructions + homemade cleaner recipes.
  • Timers, pacing (Pomodoro / Power-25), and HR targets for fitness benefits.
  • Roles & rotations (assign to household members) with streaks/rewards.
  • Inventory sync for supplies (auto low-stock alerts + make-at-home prompts).
  • Calendar and notification hooks (avoid feast days per Hebrew calendar; auto-reschedule).
  • Horizontal “raised card” layout for Session Planner + Timer + Supplies + Progress.

1) One-liners (Job → Output → Next Best Action → Events)
• Plan: “Select zones & goals → session plan + timeboxes → ‘Start Session’ → cleaning.session.started”
• Guide: “Generate chore steps → interactive checklist + tooltips → ‘Mark done’ → cleaning.step.completed”
• Pace: “Timers + voice cues + HR target → live ring & logs → ‘Pause/Resume’ → cleaning.session.updated”
• Supplies: “Check inventory → delta + make/buy list → ‘Apply/Print’ → supplies.delta.applied”
• Fitness: “Set HR target (light/moderate/vigorous) → micro-drills in steps → ‘Enable drills’ → cleaning.fitness.enabled”
• Calendar: “Block session & rotations → calendar events → ‘Sync’ → calendar.synced”
• Rewards: “Compute points/streaks → Household Board updates → ‘Redeem’ → rewards.redeemed”

