10) UI Wiring Notes
- Planner selects zones/presets → call buildCleaningPlan → setPlan().
- Checklist consumes plan.steps; each checkbox emits cleaning.step.completed.
- TimerPanel reads step durations; Power-25 default; “Power-10 sprint” option.
- SuppliesPanel shows computeSuppliesDelta result; “Apply” writes inventory patch.
- RoleAssigner writes assignments to plan.roles; ProgressPanel reads completions.
- Hebrew calendar: before sync, filter plan time windows; suggest earlier “prep day.”

11) Homemade Cleaner Recipes (cards → SuppliesPanel)
- Citrus Degreaser (do NOT use on marble/stone): Fill jar with citrus peels; cover with vinegar; steep 7–14 days; strain; 1:1 with water in spray bottle.
- Glass Cleaner: 1c water + 1c vinegar + 1 tbsp isopropyl; optional drop unscented soap; lint-free cloth.
- Soft Scrub (non-stone): 1/2c baking soda + enough castile soap to paste; optional 10ml hydrogen peroxide; patch test.
- Floor Wash (sealed wood): 1 gal warm water + few drops castile; wring nearly dry; follow with dry pass.
- Stainless Polish: tiny olive oil drop on microfiber; buff with grain; final dry cloth.

